                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-5">
                      <div class="box box-solid box-primary">
                        <div class="box-header">
                          <h3 class="box-title"> Mathematical details</h3>
                          <div class="box-tools pull-right">
                            <button class="btn btn-box-tool" data-widget="collapse">
                              <i class="fa fa-minus"></i>
                            </button>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="box-body">
                          <span class="help-block">Definition and Formula</span>
                          <script>MathJax.Hub.Queue(["Typeset", MathJax.Hub]);</script>
                          <p>The total number of enumerable combinations is:</p>

<p>\[C_{tot}= \sum_{k=0}^{N} C(N,k)=2^{N}-1\]</p>

<p>where <em>N</em> is the total number of items and <em>k</em> the desidered number of components in the combination.</p>

<p>For more theoretical details see:</p>

<p><a href="http://www.pearsonhighered.com/educator/product/Introductory-Combinatorics/9780136020400.page">Introductory Combinatorics (5th Edition), Brualdi RA</a></p>

                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-7">
                      <div class="box box-solid box-primary" style="height: auto">
                        <div class="box-header">
                          <h3 class="box-title"> Combo list</h3>
                          <div class="box-tools pull-right">
                            <button class="btn btn-box-tool" data-widget="collapse">
                              <i class="fa fa-minus"></i>
                            </button>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="box-body">
                          <span class="help-block">All possible combinations</span>
                          <div data-display-if="input.DataInput== 1">
                            <div id="SE_SPtable" style="width:100%; height:auto" class="datatables html-widget html-widget-output"></div>
                          </div>
                          <div data-display-if="input.DataInput== 5">
                            <div id="SE_SPtable_3" style="width:100%; height:auto" class="datatables html-widget html-widget-output"></div>
                          </div>
                          <div data-display-if="input.DataInput!=1">
                            <div id="SE_SPtable_2" style="width:100%; height:auto" class="datatables html-widget html-widget-output"></div>
                          </div>
                          <br/>
                          <br/>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <br/>
                  <div data-display-if="input.runButton!=0 | input.runButton_3!=0 | input.runButton_2!=0">
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-sm-8"></div>
                      <div class="shiny-html-output col-sm-3" id="kpi_summary_box_1"></div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div data-display-if="input.runButton==0 &amp; input.runButton_3==0 &amp; input.runButton_2==0">
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-sm-8"></div>
                      <div class="shiny-html-output col-sm-3" id="prova_tag"></div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
