                  </p>
                  <br/>
                  <div class="my-class" id="faq" style="height: 40px;font-family: &#39;Calibri&#39;, cursive; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.1; color: #4579B9;padding: 5px;  text-align: justify;border-style:solid none none solid;">FAQ</div>
